question - https://www.codewars.com/kata/562d8d4c434582007300004e/train/python

solution 

def obfuscate(email):
    lst = []
    for char in email:
        if char == '@':
            char = ' [at] '
        elif char == '.':
            char = ' [dot] '
        lst.append(char)
    
    return ''.join(lst)
